title: Rito... YOUR MATCHMAKING SUCKS.

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: How are those games possible? I though matchmaking was supposed to give you a fair an even match up in SOME ways.

replies.body: Respect for people actually playing Orianna :)
Orianna is my second most used support behind Thresh. Do I count?
Hell yeah man! Nice work! So many underused champs :( Yasuo, Zed, Katarina and Vayne have too much use, I wanna see more Kassadin, Poppy, Yorick, Taric, Zyra and Oriannas!
Haha. I get another point. Zyra!

looking at the stats, I'm assuming your twitch fed then afked, he only had 40 cs, you should have that at like 7 minutes, not almost 30 minutes.

looking at the rankings of all players on op.gg your team members had the advantage, they had more higher skilled players (acording to leagues, but this may not be accurate)
Oh no, Twitch did not AFK.

Mabye its his first time in ADC.
ever think of that
So you were yi... I'm guessing you didn't gank. Not your fault if every lane has no idea what they're doing though. Can't gank them all. Shit happens
